stuff that wasn't serving

00:55:37.590 --> 00:55:39.220 align:middle line:84%
the business, that
they had never

00:55:39.220 --> 00:55:40.930 align:middle line:84%
even thought about
because they've

00:55:40.930 --> 00:55:42.590 align:middle line:90%
never questioned it that way.

00:55:42.590 --> 00:55:44.470 align:middle line:84%
Usually the new stuff
is always coming in.

00:55:44.470 --> 00:55:46.070 align:middle line:90%
Deal with the new stuff.

00:55:46.070 --> 00:55:51.050 align:middle line:84%
But the old stuff sitting there
